3. Score table (Named as `Score`), with fields designed as follows:

| Field   | Type        | Constraints / Defaults                          | Description            |
|---------|-------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------|
| SNo     | varchar(10) | NOT NULL                             | Student ID (FK)    |
